text: Abryna obscura is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Bernhard Schwarzer in 1925. It is known from Taiwan and Japan.BioLib.cz - Abryna obscura. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==Subspecies== * Abryna obscura obscura Schwarzer, 1925 * Abryna obscura oshimensis Breuning, 1955 * Abryna obscura uniformis Breuning & Ohbayashi, 1966 ==References== Category:Pteropliini Category:Beetles described in 1925
title: Abryna obscura
